34
00:03:29,680 --> 00:03:41,680
Where was that seed planted of, call it insatiable skepticism and a refusal to kind of bend to authority?

35
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:50,680
Now you're asking me to psychoanalyze myself.

36
00:03:51,680 --> 00:04:04,680
On one level, I once had a editor at Discover Magazine who asked me sarcastically or facetiously whether my brother was as, quote, well adjusted as I was.

37
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:07,680
