02:14:16,680 --> 02:14:19,680
So well, this is the issue.

671
02:14:19,680 --> 02:14:35,680
One of the. Yeah, I mentioned I'm working on a book on diabetes now, and it's very much delves into the history of the field and how much I can imagine six, maybe seven people reading it once it's published.

672
02:14:36,680 --> 02:14:46,680
You think of a field like diabetes where Elliot Jocelyn opens the first diabetes clinic in the US dedicated diabetes clinic in the US around 1900.

